summary: AN ORDINANCE accepting from the State of Washington, Department of Natural Resources three easements for rights of way for storm sewer outfalls over the following State-owned land: the bed of Waterway No. 22, Plat 11, Lake Union Shore Lands; the bed of Waterway No. 5, Plate 15, Lake Washington Shore Lands; and the unplatted tide lands of the first class in front of a portion of 14th Avenue Northwest, Ballard Tide lands, all in King County, Washington.
